	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm using logarithmic shifts.
<br />
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">lda Y_TILE<br />ldx log&#40;WIDTH&#41;<br />loop:<br />asl<br />dex<br />bne loop<br /></div><br /><br />EDIT: I just thought of a faster code<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">lda Y_TILE<br />ora indication_bit<br />loop:<br />asl<br />bcc loop<br /></div>
<br />
<br />It stops shifting when it detects the indication bit.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
